ygData.messageBody:
I have been talking to the npc's in the ...... roost, (forget the first
name), it is in east freeport above the rogue guild. I was just buying some
alcohol from the npc barkeep there and some de came up and started talking to
the de Scar that spawns there sometime. I asked her what she was doing. She
told me that she heard you could play cards with him. But he says nuthing
when you hail him. I've tried many phrases but none work. Anyone now about
this or any other quest in the ....... roost?
